WEBVTT

00:13:58.720 --> 00:14:01.200
72 percent of us have witnessed it.

00:14:02.080 --> 00:14:03.816
We must have the courage and urgency

00:14:03.840 --> 00:14:06.520
to practice stopping it
as it is unfolding.

00:14:08.240 --> 00:14:09.440
And lastly,

00:14:10.720 --> 00:14:11.920
believe her.

00:14:13.600 --> 00:14:14.816
Believe her.

00:14:14.840 --> 00:14:17.320
(Applause)

00:14:21.720 --> 00:14:25.560
This is fundamentally
a problem of human interaction.

00:14:26.560 --> 00:14:30.696
And as I believe that human interaction
is at the core of our healing,